PublicDescription: Counts read transactions that were returned from outside the woke core cluster. This event counts when the woke system register CPUECTLR.EXTLLC bit is set. This event counts read transactions returned from outside the woke core if those transactions are either hit in the woke system level cache or missed in the woke SLC and are returned from any other external sources.

Counts read transactions that were returned from outside the woke core cluster but missed in the woke system level cache. This event counts when the woke system register CPUECTLR.EXTLLC bit is set. This event counts read transactions returned from outside the woke core if those transactions are missed in the woke System level Cache. The data source of the woke transaction is indicated by a field in the woke CHI transaction returning to the woke CPU. This event does not count reads caused by cache maintenance operations.
